{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-14", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "捂住耳朵", "storyInfo": "毫無目標的推進之王開始自我懷疑。深池部隊、“灰禮帽”與羅德島圍繞通訊站展開了交鋒，但最後卻發現通訊站早已被搬走。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g2_glasgowoldroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根已經帶了批人回來，正在給他們發藥。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "達格達和漢娜還在找那些可能還藏在某處廢墟裡的人。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些日子，地塊的處境你們也都知道......會在大街上露面的，已經算是極少數人了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肯定有不少人正躲在某個大樓的小隔間裡瑟瑟發抖，靠著深夜裡撿來的一點殘渣活著。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#2$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王，你要把他們都找出來？", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#8$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道我不可能救下每一個人。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但重要的是，要讓他們知道即將有一場撤離行動發生。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，大部分人在大公爵們的炮火響起的時候，不會意識到這是個離開這裡的機會，他們只會想辦法把自己藏得更好些。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他們自己選的，說不定也能活到那些薩卡茲離開這裡。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們需要知道還有其他的選擇。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，好吧，其他的選擇......", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有幾個地方，我幾天前聽到過一些動靜......但願不只是在廢墟裡刨食的野獸。", "name": "卡鐸爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_862_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，怎麼了？你的臉色不太好。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......我沒事。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......哈哈，有些不習慣。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#12$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老施特勞斯和埃米爾太太打起來了，為了一針臨時阻斷劑，一個刺瞎了另一個的眼睛。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和阿米婭費了好大勁才把他們分開，但那眼睛還是保不住了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們本來就沒帶多少藥過來，現在人們聚集在外面，有的人......很恐慌。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們覺得自己可能會被感染，也有的人根本還沒發現自己已經是個感染者了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#13$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭說，她沒有收到伊內絲約定的聯絡，她需要去確認伊內絲和博士的情況。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我一個人在下面待不下去，來這裡透口氣。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和你帶回來的那些人都很熟悉。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我從小在這裡長大，我敢打賭，別說維娜了，就連你和漢娜都沒有我熟悉諾伯特區。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#3$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候你總是沒事就在大街小巷裡閒逛。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#2$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，諾伯特區就像我的手掌，我知道每一條紋路通向哪裡。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，我......我試著去找了很多熟悉的人。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又去找了麥克拉倫，他不是不回應我們......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他聾了。我看到他的耳朵裡在淌血。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寫了字條給他，他分明應該看見了，但......他還是躲回了房間裡。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有開唱片店的卡什，以前那傢伙每次都騙我買那些過氣的爛光碟，我在他那不知道花了多少冤枉錢。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有一條腿已經完全變形了，天知道他是怎麼挪過來的。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個做進口服裝生意的布蘭達，她以前總借我看龍門的時尚雜誌。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我替她做了燒傷處理，但是......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有克萊爾，艾琳，伊東......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認識他們每一個人！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，我們回來只是為了看著這一切的嗎？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們回來到底是為了什麼？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，維娜，如果我們只能眼睜睜看著這一切發生，如果我們沒有一點改變的方法，是不是我們從一開始......就該忘了這裡？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看過那些英雄們的故事，他們了不起的冒險與旅途，他們匡扶正義，打倒邪惡——", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而英雄以外的人物，只不過是傳奇的背景板，他們的存在只是讓故事裡的主角們有個搭話的對象，有個成長的契機。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直以為我們就在這樣的故事裡，我一直為此沾沾自喜......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我認識他們每一個人，該死的，我認識他們每一個人！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不能被概括為怪物摧毀了村莊，英雄殺死了怪物那麼簡單。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是個爛俗的復仇小說。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#2$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，我與他們一起生活了二十年，他們不是英雄哀傷時念叨的幾個名字，不是殺死惡徒前幾句輕飄飄的旁白閃回。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們......他們不該......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根，我明白——", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜！亞歷山德莉娜·維娜·維多利亞！", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#11$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你回到這個國家，是為了取回屬於你的那頂了不起的王冠，締造又一位阿斯蘭王不朽的傳奇——", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#4$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是為了回家？", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，求求你，告訴我，這些都只是暫時的......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以告訴我，我們只需要再堅持一下。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "淚水從眼前這個推進之王再熟悉不過的人的臉上滾落。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她的印象裡，除了在影廳，她幾乎沒見過摩根哭的樣子。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諸王之息永遠冰冷，諸王之息永遠沉默。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，維娜，我不是在怪你......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只是走在大街上，然後一抬頭，猛然發現......", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們真的失去諾伯特區了。", "name": "摩根"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_405_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根！", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維娜，我......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友走散，房間寂靜無聲，彷彿過往的熱鬧與歡愉都是錯覺。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的陳設還是以前的樣子，和她們離開時沒什麼不同。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡什麼都不剩下了。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些日子裡，推進之王總是下意識地去觸碰那柄名為諸王之息的劍。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她又一次習慣性地把手搭在劍柄上。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她試圖從中感受到某種能量、某種激勵，就算是某種責任或註定犧牲的命運也好。"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一次又一次地失望。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己回來是為了什麼？只是經歷這一切嗎？"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是那些落在自己身上的期待的眼光根本就選錯了人，這柄劍和自己的老師只是帶給了自己太多的錯覺，讓她自以為可以成為某種象徵？"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "推進之王從未如此痛恨過自己的猶豫。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩根。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......我回來，只是為了不讓自己後悔。不讓自己在多年以後發現當初什麼都沒做。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道自己會走向哪裡......但我只是，無法忍受。", "name": "推進之王"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_112_siege_1#9$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g6_hotellobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個寓言嗎，考伯特先生？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您在試圖描述維多利亞？", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寓言？不不，我不是個說話喜歡繞彎子的人，只是些老人的懷舊情緒罷了。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們坐在這裡，總要說些話打發時間。", "name": "考伯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是更關注未來，“維多利亞的”薩卡茲。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塔拉人，你們的準備很充分，你們應該帶進來了不少人。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我猜，你們同樣不想和我鱗死網破。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你老實待在這裡，就什麼都不會發生。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想獨吞那架飛空艇的技術？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開斯特公爵派遣你進入地塊，難道是來散步的嗎？", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以共用，薩卡茲對於飛空艇的防守......想必不會太鬆懈，這對任何人都不會是一次輕鬆的任務。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果我們合作，這種技術可以不只屬於某一位大公爵，它可以屬於維多利亞。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不在乎維多利亞。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你們已經下定了決心。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你之前說過，我們對彼此的目標，都很有默契。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鑒於這種默契，我可以盡量不為難你，開斯特的寵物。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你剛才明明想殺了我。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，要我道個歉嗎？", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的任務失敗了，最多不過是降職處罰，但總歸可以保住自己的命。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你堅持想拿到開斯特公爵的表彰和提拔，可以試試。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老威靈頓的手下和他一樣固執，這次我算是領教到了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我可以待在這裡，把飛空艇的技術讓給你們。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是我也有交換的條件。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "看來你打算重新評估和我們的關係了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line216"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "形勢如此，羅德島的博士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們拒絕了我成為朋友的邀約，就只能再度淪為棋子了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會帶走國劍，溫德米爾的女兒和亞歷山德莉娜要死在這裡。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#8$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "認命了，繼承人小姐？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有收到介入這些事情的命令。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你答應了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要是已經達成的交易，開斯特公爵永遠兌現承諾。每一項承諾。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，“校官”，這是我們最大的原則。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "......", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line238"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "（伊內絲。）", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line240"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（明白。）", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們維多利亞人的壞習慣，是不是從來不問問當事人的意見？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，“灰禮帽”先生，我剛才已經說了，你的比喻很糟糕。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把我們稱作棋子，同樣也是一種比喻。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來羅德島是把和溫德米爾公爵的關係當做了自己的救命稻草？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是個好主意，你們站錯了隊。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可以一開始就不選擇站隊。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就只能——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等......", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_m", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫德米爾家的那個女孩......那是幻術和影子結合的源石技藝？！", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#4$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在哪？", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#8$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們！", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "m", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "focus": "m", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key